{"tid":1468052,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［整頓風氣］ 想每一位連登手足入一入來","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:53:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:58:23.000Z","uid":3035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2f7ac0bfa54a392bf3ad2f1f1b8adf648de770d5","tid":1468052,"uid":3035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:53:18.000Z","msg":"大家好，素未謀面，我今日第一次係連登開post<br />\n2016年11月26日正式成為連登仔。當時21歲既我好開心，因為個時HKG+討論區下左架，大家當時都變成一班無主孤魂，當晚我放學竟然發現左一個新討論區就係連登。<br />\n<br />\n由連登初開至今，我一直都有陪伴咁多位手足，係今晚我係機場發完夢番來，發現到大家係連登上既風氣極差，我就覺得不如試下發聲表達下自己意見，見到連登成為30萬人既大家庭，都好開心，仲未計數不清既cd-rom。<br />\n<br />\n但今晚真係係連登見到一個又一個令一心痛既post，不斷係到散播失敗主義論，同分化前線手足，我好驚好驚，因為好似又初見2014傘運失敗既原因，就係割蓆同分化，大家可能覺得自己網上評論可以唔洗負責任幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但前線手足可能會因為你一個comment而耿耿於懷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但有時大家一齊鳩嗡下真係幾開心。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我地依家竟然大敵當前，竟然仲同手足係到捉鬼捉鬼，內部不斷分化以下呢段我cap自伍公子既Facebook<br />\n<br />\n「不分化，不割席，但係打人就唔啱！」<br />\n「不分化，不割席，但係你阻到遊客！」<br />\n「不分化，不割席......」<br />\n<br />\n成日話民意逆轉，唔該你班撚樣照下鏡，你自己咪就係人民囉！<br />\n<br />\n啲師奶阿叔都未割席，你班撚屌已經爭住出嚟割。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家睇完有冇真正明白自己既心魔，係會影響成個運動輸或贏？ 大家成日所顧慮既民意，其實就係自己，呢場運動每一個人都係我手足，有咩事我都會幫會救，但希望大家互相尊重，互相指責，互相提醒，未必有人可能全神貫注去留意每一個細節，但大家互相提醒既時候，語氣上可唔可以好番小小，前線手足每日不斷承受既壓力，不但只體力上，仲有精神上，而連登係一個好好既平台比大家去舒緩壓力既地方。如果每日上到連登只係見到大家互相批鬥同互屌既post。大家仲會唔會仲鐘意連登呢個地方？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家同我全力推有用post.互屌既post等贏左，大家出煲底互屌，垃圾資訊全部冷處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">團結係我地人民既最大力量<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\nFILGHT FOR FREEDOM, STANDWITHHK <br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n利申，不分化，不割蓆，核彈掟中埋我都唔割，只要呢場運動可以贏"},{"pid":"08eeeaabf6d18912e995ba30f37823750baa0ed9","tid":1468052,"uid":95487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:53:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有<br />\n唔會捉得晒<br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">818見！五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bc7f0259d67138b043ebe5905701e933cb8b3a0","tid":1468052,"uid":3035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:55:47.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88723eb68ef766b39b1b66736732fd94e7a6dbf5","tid":1468052,"uid":3035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:56:16.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba9b56266721b84c1cb8a1c9db0d480428ae3bd","tid":1468052,"uid":3035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:56:27.000Z","msg":"推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"646c7836195cd663d94dd0c57c58a89649adedd0","tid":1468052,"uid":3035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:56:38.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad0027156f1530028c9629cc5f2c47ca8d123ed9","tid":1468052,"uid":3035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:57:02.000Z","msg":"推到手足見到為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a9bb771ba560d77627bfdcca10b0a5a50dcf7a6","tid":1468052,"uid":3035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:57:17.000Z","msg":"繼續推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c31a20c72fda6954ad41454ccd11f14990636a78","tid":1468052,"uid":3035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:57:35.000Z","msg":"再推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"009b0f0951a93d2af4623b9d05ff1ad2078e008b","tid":1468052,"uid":3035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:57:56.000Z","msg":"十連無難度，連登仔無能耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bb8fdfe43e660de6ff5955c9036e7ed702b03c0","tid":1468052,"uid":3035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:58:23.000Z","msg":"推爆自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}